{"tid":768982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽究竟要趕盡殺絕香港人到幾時","createTime":"2018-08-06T00:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T10:43:25.000Z","uid":183389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a5d2a6cffae36a174c5877a9fd9c23de98ce166","tid":768982,"uid":183389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:27:42.000Z","msg":"旺角去到尖沙嘴再去銅鑼灣<br />\n新聞訪問個大媽仲可以理直氣壯話自己新移民，唔識法律，一味係度強調自己無犯法，點解我地要趕盡殺絕大媽群。<br />\n<br />\n其他紮根係度的人一早已有默契，你地班大媽初黎報到就係度搞破壞，擾亂生態圈，再話人逼害你。<br />\n厚面皮到呢，又聲大夾惡，d阿叔阿伯都唔知咩心態，驅風煲老嘔湯咩，成日比飲茶錢d大媽。<br />\n<br />\n恭喜大媽成功爭取街頭賣藝賣身賺錢合法化"},{"pid":"e8830a7c4cdf803be65b89ebac28b46bfa524ca2","tid":768982,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"「香港係有自由既地方」"},{"pid":"dbabdda5c823c70ad7ac04c7cd1bef28929b65a6","tid":768982,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:30:41.000Z","msg":"人無恥則無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不斷營造個弱勢同比人恰既形象搏同情"},{"pid":"336ecc950ab0c1d31c5b8c85e4977bc1d979b18c","tid":768982,"uid":183389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8830a7c4cdf803be65b89ebac28b46bfa524ca2","tid":768982,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"「香港係有自由既地方」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:31:43.000Z","msg":"岩啊 所以幾唔中意大媽 都無野可以做到<br />\n破壞左自由同上面有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n根本呢個就係一個局 一個圈套"},{"pid":"3562fdf443de513c6f5e008bef5c59914b46ba3f","tid":768982,"uid":192813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:33:24.000Z","msg":"返大灣區唱啦屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe76960d52e30afc2ccfc3d740bbebd6cbbe2b0","tid":768982,"uid":183389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"正苦做好d文創配套<br />\n比大媽選個代表去西九xiqu做表演發聲<br />\n保育大媽文化<br />\n<br />\n大媽掛住選代表仲唔狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />